{"id": 2090, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X大众汽车】曾经出现过哪一瞬，让你觉得生活突然就被点亮？", "description": "周日晚上死去活来的时候刮起了台风，周一放假。", "record_count": 12432, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171227121641uyvd3WrU8Aa0hzgD.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 256770, "content": "梦中梦到自己喜欢的人也喜欢自己，梦醒了之后，她果真也喜欢着我。", "image": "img/option/option/201712271225506WpkJfLOGdAxrQnF", "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223472}, {"id": 257282, "content": "瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982578}, {"id": 256771, "content": "当自己都绝望放弃的时候，另一半温暖的拥抱", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221161}, {"id": 258307, "content": "和好了\n瘦了\n有钱了\n要做的事情都做了，只能玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231179}, {"id": 256772, "content": "夕阳西下，照在身上暖暖的", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223475}, {"id": 256773, "content": "ca，远光灯！", "image": null, "praise_count": 303, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899562}, {"id": 257285, "content": "火锅\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115002}, {"id": 256774, "content": "想要的都有，没有的不奢求", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223479}, {"id": 256775, "content": "本来以为自己不会是幸运的了，每次挫折都可以装作无所谓。然后小小幸运下都会觉得哇。我也可以这么幸运", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223478}, {"id": 256776, "content": "低头发现脚边有张25元的钞票", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597528}, {"id": 256777, "content": "翻东西的时候突然翻到了小时候的某件纪念品，比如老师发的小红花，比如那个人的字。", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223485}, {"id": 256779, "content": "整理旧记事本，翻到好多年前老友对自己和未来的寄语。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939195}, {"id": 256780, "content": "清楚记得小时候 有一次没钱的时候 突然在某本书里翻出了不知道什么时候夹进去的十块钱 一下子感觉整个世界都明亮了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 256781, "content": "在幼儿园当实习老师，技能也不好，带班也不行，可是小朋友冲过来抱我的时候，心里真是暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911164}, {"id": 257293, "content": "喜欢的人居然也爱着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013834}, {"id": 256782, "content": "和朋友同时发送同一句话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165192}, {"id": 256783, "content": "突然的旅行✈️！", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220103}, {"id": 257039, "content": "你出现了以后", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939196}, {"id": 257295, "content": "烘出一只惊艳的豆子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279810}, {"id": 256784, "content": "街上看到一个美丽的笑容！不知道TA在笑什么，但现在已经不去追问。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980503}, {"id": 259088, "content": "天气预报有雨 第二天晴天！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220103}, {"id": 256785, "content": "突如其来的希望都是自己给自己的，死不了就得自己去点亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017999}, {"id": 257297, "content": "遇见一个让自己日思夜想的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104136}, {"id": 256786, "content": "在下班回家的地铁上，跟陌生人不小心对视，然后两个人都笑了 ：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222759}, {"id": 261138, "content": "想吃榴莲转角看见水果店", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330251}, {"id": 256787, "content": "终于把喜欢的东热猪脚和名字对上了号。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212802}, {"id": 256788, "content": "做完自己不喜欢的事。。。发现还有很多时间剩下来可以看看书，看看动漫，可以自己消遣，这样就十分满足了", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1162856}, {"id": 256789, "content": "自己脑子里闪过的想法算吗？有时会告诉自己要做真正的改变，要获取价值的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913697}, {"id": 257045, "content": "把裤子放进洗衣机前，翻口袋找到一张人民币", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375024}, {"id": 256790, "content": "他出现的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223518}, {"id": 256791, "content": "刚到车站，车就来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 332, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212230}, {"id": 256792, "content": "很久没穿的衣服口袋里找到了钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514972}, {"id": 257304, "content": "从许久没穿裤兜或者包包里发现竟然一把钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225615}, {"id": 256793, "content": "爱上一个人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223529}, {"id": 256795, "content": "想吃的东西，懒得动。被别人送到了手边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201453}, {"id": 256800, "content": "走在路上，路灯突然一盏接一盏的亮起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223545}, {"id": 257056, "content": "我想和她说话，她刚好在", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 257312, "content": "发现自己爱的人原来是个人渣，下一秒找到了真爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224511}, {"id": 256801, "content": "当我努力很久的东西终于换来一个比较好的结果时", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223548}, {"id": 257313, "content": "吃到可好吃可好吃可好吃的食物  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198175}, {"id": 256802, "content": "找到了那首萦绕在脑海的旋律", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223542}, {"id": 257058, "content": "着急赶时间的时候，一路绿灯没有堵车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790711}, {"id": 256803, "content": "突然有钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221745}, {"id": 256804, "content": "喜欢的对象突然来找我", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223559}, {"id": 256805, "content": "突然放晴的天空、河边新出的柳芽儿、不认识的人跟自己打招呼、邻座的宝宝露出笑容、陌生的地方发现美景、迷路的下一秒看到警察，还有秋叶正巧落在肩头、窗外大雪纷飞、买到了很想吃的冰淇淋、想你的时候正好收到你的简讯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613298}, {"id": 257317, "content": "觉得要迟到，后来醒了过来，还有大把时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225709}, {"id": 256807, "content": "突然发现自己还会为一些事感动地流泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014749}, {"id": 257319, "content": "跟朋友或家人深聊后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198732}, {"id": 256808, "content": "一个微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533581}, {"id": 259112, "content": "他说他爱我的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236679}]}